ECONOMIC_OPERATORS_PERSONAL_SITUATION.P: The Contracting Authority shall exclude from the public procurement contract awarding procedure each economic operator in the following cases:
— in the last 5 years there was an effective conviction for participation in criminal organization, corruption, fraud or money laundering,
— there is minor penalty that prohibits participation in procedures for public announcement, awarding contracts on public procurements and contract for public-private partnership,
— there is effective conviction for temporary or permanent prohibition to perform certain activity,
— has initiated open bankruptcy procedure or liquidation procedure,

— has unpaid taxes, contributions and other public fees, except if the economic operator has deferred payments for those taxes, contributions and other public fees in accordance with the special regulations and the same are regularly paid,

— there is effective conviction by which infringement sanction has been imposed on - interdiction for professional activities, activities or duties, i.e. temporary interdiction of separate activity realization and,
— provides false information or does not submit the information requested by the Contracting Authority.
For proving personal standing, the economic operator submits the following documents:
— Statement of economic operator that in the last 5 years there was no effective conviction for participation in criminal organization, corruption, fraud or money laundering,
— Certificate that any competent authority has initiated no open bankruptcy procedure,
— Certificate that any competent authority has initiated no open liquidation procedure,
— Certificate for paid taxes, contributions and other public payments by competent authority in the country where the economic operator has been registered in,

— Certificate from the Register of penalties for crimes committed by legal persons that there is no minor penalty that prohibits participation in procedures for public announcement, awarding contracts on public procurements and contract for public-private partnership,
— Certificate from Register of penalties for crimes committed by legal persons that there is no effective conviction for temporary or permanent prohibition to perform certain activity,

— Certificate that there is no effective conviction by which infringement sanction has been imposed on — interdiction for professional activities, activities or duties, i.e. temporary interdiction of separate activity realization.

T_CAPACITY_INFORMATION.P: — For registered medicines: The economic operator for the offered goods needs to have approval for putting into circulation the medicine or temporary or permanent approval for parallel import, in accordance with the Law on medicines and medical devices,

— For unregistered medicines: The economic operator for the offered goods needs to have a document that allows import (approval for intervention import) according to the Law on medicines and medical devices.

T_CAPACITY_MIN_LEVEL.P: — For registered medicines: Decision for putting into circulation the ready medicine or a temporary or permanent approval for parallel import, in accordance with the Law on medicines and medical devices,
— For unregistered medicines: Import licence (approval for intervention import) in accordance with the Law on medicines and medical devices.
